destructor Destroy; override;
Destroys an instance of TDomNode and all of its children. The TDomNode is automatically removed from its parent node and detached from its owner document (if any).
Do not call Destroy directly in an application. Instead, call Free. Free verifies that the TDomNode reference is not nil, and only then calls Destroy.

